<ol>
  <li>
    <p>But he knew that <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="any conventional slip | conventional - of traditional design"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(任何一个寻常的疏忽)</code></b>, the slightest nostalgic indiscretion, could revive the unpleasant taste of the past in her heart.</p>
